(window["webpackJsonp"]=window["webpackJsonp"]||[]).push([["chunk-2d0ce7ec"],{6062:function(a){a.exports=JSON.parse('{"title":"Where the Heart Is","header":"Rumor has it that, at this time of year, Sharona changes into a special outfit and sets off for a mystery location. This time, an opportunity to uncover the secret of her annual ritual presents itself to you...","chat":[{"chat":[{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Back in Gannon City again."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Vice is making her regular report... and that could take ages."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Let\'s see... Maybe I can go back to the Colossus and get a few more minutes of sleep..."},{"char":"Charon:","dialogue":"This is the third time you have rejected me, my comrade!"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"That\'s right."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The public airship is out of the question for me, let alone that earth-shaking train of yours..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Hmm? It\'s Sharona and Charon..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Sharona looks a little different when she\'s not in combat..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I should go say hi."},{"char":"Charon:","dialogue":"Ah! \'Tis you, Caelestite! My dearest friend!"},{"char":"Charon:","dialogue":"Since you are here, would you mind assisting me in persuading my dear Commander to agree on a method of travel?"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The Caelestite being here makes no difference, Charon."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"My answer remains the same: that train of yours is unbearable to ride."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I\'ll find a way to repair my airship..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(Seems like Sharona wants to go somewhere, and wants to travel alone...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(Her airship is down, and she can\'t use public transportation or Other End...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Um, Commander Sharona...?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"M-Maybe I can... lend a hand?"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Don\'t you have other things to do, Caelestite?"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Or do you honestly think your Colossus draws less attention than Charon\'s train?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Eh... K-Kind of?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"At least Soroz doesn\'t blast strange music while traveling."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"...You have a point."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"In any case, this is my own problem."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"But you\'re in a real bind right now, aren\'t you?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I promise I won\'t stick my nose in your personal affairs... That\'s your business, not mine."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"But I really think I can help you with your transportation dilemma."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"You\'re more than welcome to refuse, of course..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"In the end, it\'s up to you. I just wanted to give you another option."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"...Alright."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Then let\'s get moving."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"A-Already?! That was fast!"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"What, going back on your word already?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I\'m not!"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Then let\'s go."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"W-Wait for me...!"},{"char":"Charon:","dialogue":"Now that I think about it... Every year, without fail, Sharona dresses this way and leaves for an undisclosed location."},{"char":"Charon:","dialogue":"I wonder what it could mean... What divinity could be guiding the actions of the Lastborn of Laden?"},{"char":"Charon:","dialogue":"...Hmm? Where has the Caelestite gone?"},{"char":"Charon:","dialogue":"Ho-ho! I am quite looking forward to today\'s show!"},{"char":"Outside of Umbraton, in an isolated valley...","dialogue":"We\'re almost at the location you requested."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Are you sure this is the right place, Sharona?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"It looks completely barren..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"This is the right place."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Huh... It looks kind of familiar, now that I think about it."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"This is... This is right below Lumopolis, isn\'t it?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Yes."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"This hidden area can also be used to escape from an Eclipsite invasion."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Yeah... It seems like a nice place. Really quiet and serene..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Mostly..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"When we get to our destination, wait outside for me."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I... I won\'t be long, I promise."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"If you see any signs of danger. Call for me, and I\'ll come right out."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The rest is none of your concern."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"That\'s the plan for this trip. Any questions, Caelestite?"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"...N-No, I got it!"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Good. Now then... Let\'s get going."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Alright... We\'re here."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I\'m going in."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"She left so quickly..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Now that I\'m alone, this place does feel a little creepy."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"It\'s cold..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"It\'s quiet... Too quiet. It\'s almost unbearable..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I think I\'ll stand closer to the entrance..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Graaagh!"},{"char":"???:","dialogue":"So they\'ve found their way into this place, too..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Graaagh!"},{"char":"???:","dialogue":"Oh no, is that... the smell of Eclipsites?!"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"There are sounds of fighting coming from the inside..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Sharona\'s in there all by herself! I have to go help her!"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"This place... is a cemetery?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"It\'s strangely quiet now... Is the battle already over?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Sharona! Sharona!!"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"If you can hear me, please say something!"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Sharo--"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I\'m here, Caelestite."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Whoa..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"What is this place, Sharona? Are those...?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Nothing worth mentioning. These are murals, nothing more."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"They\'re beautiful... no, shocking!"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I can\'t explain it, but I\'m starting to get goosebumps."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Are you hurt?"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"No."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"That\'s good."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Sharona... Just what is this place?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"The people in these murals... Their clothes look kind of familiar."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"They do, don\'t they?"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"They\'re from Lumopolis."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Lumopolis?! But haven\'t you always been..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Against Lumopolis\' stubborn, old ways?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"If so, why would you choose to come here? This place... if I\'m right, it\'s a cemetery for the nobility of Lumopolis."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"......"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I honestly thought you would have used your powers to figure out the truth by now, Caelestite."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"This is the final resting place of my clansmen."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The land beneath your feet is fertilized by the blood and bones of the noble Kartima Family."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"They should have been laid to rest in the heavenly kingdom of the White Night up high..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"But unfortunately, because of the incident..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"A power struggle that lacked proper documentation, and was riddled with fake records."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The Kartima Family has been branded as traitors ever since."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The living members were exiled, and the departed couldn\'t even rest in peace."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"They weren\'t even granted the mercy of being interred in their own cemetery. All they could do was implore the more sympathetic families to aid them in secret..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"...And so, they were laid to rest here."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"How ironic..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The ancestors of the Kartima Family sacrificed their blood and lives to protect Lumopolis, but now... They have been all but forgotten by the people."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The empire has forgotten that its present glory was built upon the blood of dragons."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The White Night up high..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"But blood and bones below."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I\'m so sorry..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I didn\'t mean to pry..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Please accept my apologies, Sharona... You and your family."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"As an outsider, I\'ve disturbed their slumber."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"They are not my family."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"But your name..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"You really think that we\'re a family just because we share a surname?"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Sharona Kartima..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"They are my clansmen, but they are not my family."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"They have no way of telling me the truth about my parents\' death, and I can\'t pretend that I\'m not connected to them somehow, either."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Your parents..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I don\'t even remember them anymore."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"When it comes to the Kartima Family, the thing that left the deepest impression on me..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Happened on the day of the genocide."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Just before he died, a well-respected elder in the family told me..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"To always remember my name, and to never give up the search for the secret of my bloodline."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Prior to that, I didn\'t even deserve to greet the man at family gatherings."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Then... have you discovered the secret of your bloodline yet?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I have searched for a long, long time, but... I still haven\'t found the answer."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I don\'t even know why I was entrusted with this impossible task in the first place."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Just because I\'m the last surviving member of our family, I\'m expected to carry the burden of our bloodline\'s secret history?"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Fragments of the past constantly surge through my mind, bringing an endless stream of hatred..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"...This isn\'t fair."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I\'m sorry..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I really didn\'t mean to ask about you and your clan\'s past..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"If you hadn\'t brought me here, you would never have known."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Yeah..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Wait... Family! That\'s right!"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Illumina! The Illumina Federation!"}],"branch":[{"text":"They\'re your real home, aren\'t they, Sharona?","link":"1"},{"text":"No, Illumina doesn\'t count either...","link":"2"}]},{"chat":[{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"...My home?"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Home is somewhere that loves me unconditionally and asks for nothing in return."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"My relationship with Illumina... It was built on the trust from the Grand Marshal."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Though, in return, I am granted considerable power..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Sometimes, I do find myself saying... That maybe this place is my home."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(What does home truly mean...?)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(I have never lived in Eraveil myself, but...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(I can say, with full certainty, that Eraveil is my home.)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(And Soroz... He\'s not just my shelter, but also my friend. I was never truly alone growing up...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(And I\'ve made all kinds of friends since.)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(But to Sharona... Where would home be for her?)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(I never got to know any of my relatives, but I\'m positive their love for me was real.)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(Sharona grew up surrounded by family, but still doesn\'t know where home is...)"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I\'ve said too much."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Thank you for your help, Caelestite."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"D-Don\'t mention it."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I\'m sure all of this must be confusing for you."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"After all, why would I be here paying my respects if they aren\'t my family?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I think... You\'re trying to get to the bottom of what happened in the past, right?"}],"branch":[{"text":"Restart Story","link":"0"},{"text":"The truth behind your clan?","link":"4"},{"text":"The secret of your bloodline?","link":"5"}]},{"chat":[{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I agree, for the most part."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The meaning of home is far more profound."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"A home provides a deep and inseparable sense of love..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Whereas in Illumina, I work only to live up to the trust and expectations of others."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Though, in return, I am granted considerable power..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Sometimes, I do find myself saying... That maybe this place is my home."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(What does home truly mean...?)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(I have never lived in Eraveil myself, but...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(I can say, with full certainty, that Eraveil is my home.)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(And Soroz... He\'s not just my shelter, but also my friend. I was never truly alone growing up...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(And I\'ve made all kinds of friends since.)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(But to Sharona... Where would home be for her?)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(I never got to know any of my relatives, but I\'m positive their love for me was real.)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(Sharona grew up surrounded by family, but still doesn\'t know where home is...)"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I\'ve said too much."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Thank you for your help, Caelestite."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"D-Don\'t mention it."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I\'m sure all of this must be confusing for you."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"After all, why would I be here paying my respects if they aren\'t my family?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I think... You\'re trying to get to the bottom of what happened in the past, right?"}],"branch":[{"text":"Restart Story","link":"0"},{"text":"The truth behind your clan?","link":"4"},{"text":"The secret of your bloodline?","link":"5"}]},{"chat":[{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Though, in return, I am granted considerable power..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Sometimes, I do find myself saying... That maybe this place is my home."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(What does home truly mean...?)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(I have never lived in Eraveil myself, but...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(I can say, with full certainty, that Eraveil is my home.)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(And Soroz... He\'s not just my shelter, but also my friend. I was never truly alone growing up...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(And I\'ve made all kinds of friends since.)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(But to Sharona... Where would home be for her?)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(I never got to know any of my relatives, but I\'m positive their love for me was real.)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(Sharona grew up surrounded by family, but still doesn\'t know where home is...)"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I\'ve said too much."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Thank you for your help, Caelestite."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"D-Don\'t mention it."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"I\'m sure all of this must be confusing for you."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"After all, why would I be here paying my respects if they aren\'t my family?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I think... You\'re trying to get to the bottom of what happened in the past, right?"}],"branch":[{"text":"Restart Story","link":"0"},{"text":"The truth behind your clan?","link":"4"},{"text":"The secret of your bloodline?","link":"5"}]},{"chat":[{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Yes."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"As well as our connection to dragons."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The screaming fragments of my memories... of true dragons."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"But until I discover the truth behind it all..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"All I can do is come here to pay my respects every year, in hopes of feeling something..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Because we share a surname, I am never truly alone."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Even if... I don\'t consider them my family."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(Family...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Sharona... Please offer my respects to them in my place."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Let\'s go."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Before we leave... There is something that I must ask of you."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Sure."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Caelestite... I ask that you refrain from disclosing the location of this place to anyone else."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"As far as my understanding of the people of Lumopolis goes..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"They are quick to forget kindness, but will never forget a grudge."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Especially not a grudge held against the traitorous Kartima Family..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Their hatred will never truly disappear."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"This, I fear, is the only thing I share in common with the people of Lumopolis."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"It\'s always there... The familiar sense of hatred, constantly making my blood boil..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I promise."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"What a touching moment..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"If it were truly that touching, then why aren\'t you crying?"},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Cry? Why would I cry?"},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Don\'t make me laugh."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"...You\'re late, Leona."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Late? They aren\'t worthy of my visit, let alone my punctuality."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"That outfit of yours..."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Still trying to follow in their long-dead traditions, Sharona?"},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"No one in the world besides me recognizes that outfit as the Kartima Family\'s formal attire."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Then as long as we\'re alive, and I have this outfit..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The Kartima Family hasn\'t been completely abandoned by history."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Hmph... How naive."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"What\'s the point of these formalities and tributes, if we\'re doomed to repeat the same mistakes?"},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"But you already know that perfectly well, don\'t you... little sister?"},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"There\'s no escaping this fate. Someday, we\'ll be lying cold and dead in this place, too."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"The only difference is that, when we\'re gone, nobody will be there to wear those clothes and pay their respects to us."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"...It doesn\'t matter."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Oh, dear sister... your understanding of destiny is so pitifully shallow."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"But I think..."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"There\'s someone here with a much deeper understanding of the word destiny..."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Isn\'t that right... The lonely Caelestite?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"...Me?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I\'m not alone at all!"},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Is that so, kiddo? I envy your confidence."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"I just hope you never stop feeling that way..."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Now, my sweeties. I have to say goodbye."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"She went inside, Sharona..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Sharona? Sharona!"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"...Let\'s go."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Back to... Illumina."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"...Sure. Let\'s go back together."},{"char":"The next day.","dialogue":"Navigator? Hey, Navigator! Are you feeling okay?"},{"char":"Vice:","dialogue":"Uh... Huh?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"What\'s on your mind? Do you need some fresh air? Come on, let\'s go for a walk around Gannon City!"},{"char":"Vice:","dialogue":"N-Nothing\'s on my mind, really..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Hey, Vice... what does the word home mean to you?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Huh? If I had to say..."},{"char":"Vice:","dialogue":"The Colossus is my home, and so is Illumina."},{"char":"Vice:","dialogue":"Anywhere that I can live comfortably is a place I can call home."},{"char":"Vice:","dialogue":"Yeah..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"A comfortable place..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(For Sharona, home is a place she can always return to. It\'s where she belongs."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(Devoting herself to Illumina...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(Is her way of resisting destiny and finding a home.)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(I just wonder...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(If the Colossus will ever feel like home to her?)"}],"branch":[{"text":"Restart Story","link":"0"}]},{"chat":[{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Yes."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Maybe after I uncover the secrets of the Kartima Family..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The truth behind the past, and the answer to the fragments of hatred in my mind... Maybe all will be revealed then."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"But until I discover the truth behind it all..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"All I can do is come here to pay my respects every year, in hopes of feeling something..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Because we share a surname, I am never truly alone."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Even if... I don\'t consider them my family."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(Family...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Sharona... Please offer my respects to them in my place."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Let\'s go."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Before we leave... There is something that I must ask of you."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Sure."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Caelestite... I ask that you refrain from disclosing the location of this place to anyone else."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"As far as my understanding of the people of Lumopolis goes..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"They are quick to forget kindness, but will never forget a grudge."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Especially not a grudge held against the traitorous Kartima Family..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Their hatred will never truly disappear."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"This, I fear, is the only thing I share in common with the people of Lumopolis."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"It\'s always there... The familiar sense of hatred, constantly making my blood boil..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I promise."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"What a touching moment..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"If it were truly that touching, then why aren\'t you crying?"},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Cry? Why would I cry?"},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Don\'t make me laugh."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"...You\'re late, Leona."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Late? They aren\'t worthy of my visit, let alone my punctuality."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"That outfit of yours..."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Still trying to follow in their long-dead traditions, Sharona?"},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"No one in the world besides me recognizes that outfit as the Kartima Family\'s formal attire."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Then as long as we\'re alive, and I have this outfit..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"The Kartima Family hasn\'t been completely abandoned by history."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Hmph... How naive."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"What\'s the point of these formalities and tributes, if we\'re doomed to repeat the same mistakes?"},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"But you already know that perfectly well, don\'t you... little sister?"},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"There\'s no escaping this fate. Someday, we\'ll be lying cold and dead in this place, too."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"The only difference is that, when we\'re gone, nobody will be there to wear those clothes and pay their respects to us."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"...It doesn\'t matter."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Oh, dear sister... your understanding of destiny is so pitifully shallow."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"But I think..."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"There\'s someone here with a much deeper understanding of the word destiny..."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Isn\'t that right... The lonely Caelestite?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"...Me?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"I\'m not alone at all!"},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Is that so, kiddo? I envy your confidence."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"I just hope you never stop feeling that way..."},{"char":"Leona:","dialogue":"Now, my sweeties. I have to say goodbye."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"She went inside, Sharona..."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Sharona? Sharona!"},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"...Let\'s go."},{"char":"Sharona:","dialogue":"Back to... Illumina."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"...Sure. Let\'s go back together."},{"char":"The next day.","dialogue":"Navigator? Hey, Navigator! Are you feeling okay?"},{"char":"Vice:","dialogue":"Uh... Huh?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"What\'s on your mind? Do you need some fresh air? Come on, let\'s go for a walk around Gannon City!"},{"char":"Vice:","dialogue":"N-Nothing\'s on my mind, really..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Hey, Vice... what does the word home mean to you?"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"Huh? If I had to say..."},{"char":"Vice:","dialogue":"The Colossus is my home, and so is Illumina."},{"char":"Vice:","dialogue":"Anywhere that I can live comfortably is a place I can call home."},{"char":"Vice:","dialogue":"Yeah..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"A comfortable place..."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(For Sharona, home is a place she can always return to. It\'s where she belongs."},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(Devoting herself to Illumina...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(Is her way of resisting destiny and finding a home.)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(I just wonder...)"},{"char":"Navigator:","dialogue":"(If the Colossus will ever feel like home to her?)"}],"branch":[{"text":"Restart Story","link":"0"}]}]}')}}]);
